land shark
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:[used elsewhere but sign.in NZ] a person who exploited others in the rush to claim land [mid-late 1800s.]
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
